com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.annotation

Class SymbolManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.annotation.AnnotationManager<Symbol,SymbolOptions,OnSymbolClickListener,OnSymbolLongClickListener>
      • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.annotation.SymbolManager

  • public class SymbolManager
extends AnnotationManager<Symbol,SymbolOptions,OnSymbolClickListener,OnSymbolLongClickListener>
    The symbol manager allows to add symbols to a map.
